</ul>

<p>The API supports both detection and humanization endpoints, with detailed documentation and SDKs for popular programming languages.</p>

<h2>Privacy and Security in AI Writing Tools</h2>
<p>When using any AI writing tool — whether for generation, detection, or humanization — privacy should be a top concern. You may be submitting sensitive academic work, proprietary business content, or personal writing to these platforms.</p>

